:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacdad9bcb450a6328273d34938957f8d1b37832","tid":1383513,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人加油！<br />\n堅持我地既信念！<br />\nDo the right things!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4beb2d2f4684a66b449d9dd2c27d8c9f9c6bf70b","tid":1383513,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decfc39ee8d22aad13b2dd1a3044db4d6f175594","tid":1383513,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d2f846a053499a8e61e551436804b925144911","tid":1383513,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"全民8月5曰大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"9d70f7f0439365ceed8f7c5b14e7d6ea1b97a252","tid":1383513,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69ea15f1e13eedd0ac28f35c7c09d6442829c98","tid":1383513,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"對對對，得罪咗人就唔好，要敬而遠之。"},{"pid":"7361eb1a8bbce3c34c7b32b5618c611b533b7647","tid":1383513,"uid":120057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"唔好侮辱啲狗唔該"},{"pid":"163b6400b060e2432a648c0df0c3a201f782f13a","tid":1383513,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">社會抹殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n_______________________<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"0b0ad830d905622f4a193d052fbf619368bce71c","tid":1383513,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f50b89df9dfed3ee0ffa005a5d4b83308ccd22","tid":1383513,"uid":144492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:00:57.000Z","msg":"啲狗仔女實打鳩人啦你咁<br />\n打完見家長仲兇返個老師轉頭<br />\n而家克警大撚哂㗎嘛"},{"pid":"e693026ed548909b74dadb60b76dfd800f827ad8","tid":1383513,"uid":55519,"like":9,"dislike":0,